c: 7
v: 142
t: "Ne khwalaka Musa tsinyanga amakhumi kataru ne nikhumetakhwo ekhumi, nibiula ebise bia Nyasaye wuwe tsinyanga amakhumi kane. Mana Musa Naboolela Omusiani wabu, Haruni mbu: “Tila habundu wanje okhwimilila Abandu banje ne obe omulayi, ne olalonda tsinjila tsiabalia bakholanga obubii tawe.”"